title: Diana Ross jets out of LA to finish Las Vegas residency | Daily Mail Online
text: Share Diana teamed it with leggings and sneakers, black of course. The Endless Love hitmaker's raven black hair was styled in a mass of curls and she wore dark glasses to protect her eyes from the bright sunlight. Ready to to rock (and roll): The 72-year-old star was due to perform the last three dates of her residency at The Venetian Jet-set chic: The Aint No Mountain High Enough hitmaker was casually dressed black from tip to toe for her 45-minute flight The smiling celebrity accessorized with a pair of long-tasseled statement earrings in silver that draped down to her shoulders. Proud grandmother Diana likely spent some time with her 18-month-old granddaughter Jagger while she was in Los Angeles, The tot is her 28-year-old son Evan Ross's first child with wife Ashlee Simpson. The couple married in 2014. Traveling light: The star clutched her purse and her phone so presumably someone else was dealing with her luggage Shining star: She started her nine-date The Essential Diana Ross: Some Memories Never Fade residency at The Venetian earlier this month and will wrap it Saturday night Meanwhile, Elton John, who also has a residency in Vegas, caught Diana's show at The Venetian and seemed to enjoy it immensely. 'Saw Diana Ross tonight. The lady was simply sensational. Her voice is better than ever. Amazing set list. Kick ass band. And not a dancer in sight,' the Tiny Dancer singer captioned an Instagram snap of himself with the icon. Diana is set to complete her nine-date The Essential Diana Ross: Some Memories Never Fade residency at The Venetian on Friday and Saturday. The generous star donates one dollar from every ticket sold to her Diana Ross Charitable Foundation. He's a fan: Elton John, who also has a Vegas residency, caught Diana's show and gushed about it on Instagram, saying, 'The lady was simply sensational. Her voice is better than ever' Proud grandmother: Diana likely spent some time with 18-month-old granddaughter Jagger while in LA. The tot is her son Evan Ross' first child with wife Ashlee Simpson.
